description: <Window x:Class="BakeryManagement.MainWindow" xmlns="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2006/xaml/presentation" xmlns:x="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2006/xaml" Title="Product Management" Height="450" Width="800"><Grid><DataGrid x:Name="ProductDataGrid" AutoGenerateColumns="False" SelectionMode="Single" SelectionUnit="FullRow" IsReadOnly="True" SelectionChanged="ProductDataGrid_SelectionChanged"><DataGrid.Columns><DataGridTextColumn Header="ID" Binding="{Binding ProductID}" /><DataGridTextColumn Header="Наименование" Binding="{Binding ProductName}" /><DataGridTextColumn Header="Количество" Binding="{Binding QuantityInStock}" /><DataGridTextColumn Header="Дата производства" Binding="{Binding ProductionDate}" /><DataGridTextColumn Header="Срок годности" Binding="{Binding ExpiryDate}" /></DataGrid.Columns></DataGrid><StackPanel Orientation="Vertical" Margin="10"><TextBox x:Name="ProductIDTextBox" Visibility="Collapsed" /><TextBox x:Name="ProductNameTextBox" PlaceholderText="Наименование" /><TextBox x:Name="QuantityInStockTextBox" PlaceholderText="Количество" /><TextBox x:Name="ProductionDateTextBox" PlaceholderText="Дата производства" /><TextBox x:Name="ExpiryDateTextBox" PlaceholderText="Срок годности" /><Button Content="Сохранить изменения" Click="SaveButton_Click" /><Button Content="Удалить товар" Click="DeleteButton_Click" /></StackPanel></Grid></Window>
